    "",
    "file_index: zero-based index used by load_file_from_main_menu to pick which",
    "  in-game save file to load. 0 = File 1 (HQ intro start), 1 = File 2, etc.",
    "",
    "action_index: zero-based DOWN-presses before SPACE on the verb/action menu.",
    "target_index: zero-based DOWN-presses before SPACE on the target submenu.",
    "repeat: how many times to execute the same action+target (default 1).",
    "",
    "action_index mapping empirically verified via explore_menu.py on the rasu scene:",
    "  0=移動(Move)  1=見る(Look)  2=話す(Talk)  3=調べる(Examine)  4=考える(Think)",
    "Context-specific verbs (浴びる/昇る/聞く/乱入する/脱ぐ/使う/開ける/搭乗) appear",
    "at varying positions — steps using them have action_index=99 as a placeholder;",
    "the OCR out-of-range check will stop safely so you can fill in the real index.",
    "",
    "For chained Move steps ('移動 廊下→控室') each arrow is its own step.",
    "target_index values are best guesses; verify with explore_menu.py."
